The paper deals with aspect-based sentiment analysis, which is a subtask of sentiment analysis. The use of BERT for fine-tuning a pre-trained model is a common technique in natural language processing, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, the paper involves machine learning techniques such as question answering (cs.AI), natural language inference (cs.CL), and optimization (cs.LG). The paper also involves information retrieval techniques such as text classification (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
